# arvo-bits

Bit-level primitives for arvo numeric types. BitWidth, BitAccess,
BitSequence trait contracts. Semantic aliases (Bit, Byte, Word, DWord,
QWord). Blanket impls for all arvo fixed-point types. Opaque-bit
concrete container (Bits, parameterised by const N) for fixed-width
non-arithmetic identity values. Bit-count const-generic positions take
`BitWidth` from arvo L0; bare `u8` is not in the public surface.
`#![no_std]`, no alloc.
